  "text": "Two structural models for a non-axisymmetric terminator design, the Backward Bent Duct Buoy (BBDB) [CITATION_1] , are discussed in this report. The results of this structural model design study are intended to inform experiments and modeling underway in support of the U.S. Department of Energy (DOE) initiated Reference Model Project (RMP).",
